you were married?

273
00:21:25,064 --> 00:21:28,397
- You never asked.
- He knows about us.

274
00:21:28,434 --> 00:21:30,402
He does and he doesn't.

275
00:21:30,436 --> 00:21:32,404
He chooses
what he wants to know.

276
00:21:32,438 --> 00:21:35,407
