to the truth, Anders.

436
00:33:49,641 --> 00:33:51,609
Lock him up.

437
00:33:51,643 --> 00:33:53,611
We'll do this the hard way.

438
00:33:53,645 --> 00:33:56,136
Open up.

439
00:34:09,728 --> 00:34:11,696
Oy, you. Out!

440
00:34:17,902 --> 00:34:20,234
Morning, Officers.
What a beautiful day!

441
00:34:20,271 --> 00:34:23,069
l don't know who you've
got pulling strings for you, Anders.

442
00:34:23,108 --> 00:34:25,099
But this isn't over.

443
00:34:26,678 --> 00:34:28,646
l hate to see
an unhappy policeman.

444
00:34:28,680 --> 00:34:30,648
l admire you.
Straight up, l do.

445
00:34:30,682 --> 00:34:32,650
You've got big balls.

446
00:34:32,684 --> 00:34:35,778
l couldn't put all my money
into a place like yours.

447
00:34:35,820 --> 00:34:38,812
l'd be worried about
fire safety inspections,

448
00:34:38,857 --> 00:34:42,054
keeping my drinks license,
drug busts,

449
00:34:42,093 --> 00:34:44,721
add in a rap for letting
hookers use the place

450
00:34:44,763 --> 00:34:46,822
in-between clients.

451
00:34:48,666 --> 00:34:51,191
Now look what you've done.

452
00:34:51,236 --> 00:34:54,205
You've frightened me so much,
l'm spilling my tea.

453
00:35:03,214 --> 00:35:07,082
# Don't worry about me #

454
00:35:07,118 --> 00:35:08,779
# l get along... #

455
00:35:08,820 --> 00:35:11,118
How many more people
have l got to tell?

456
00:35:11,156 --> 00:35:13,420
Anders, Harry Anders.

457
00:35:13,458 --> 00:35:15,926
Mrs. Mansdorf is
not available--

458
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,928
lt's important.
l have to talk to her.

459
00:35:17,962 --> 00:35:21,398
l'm sorry, sir, but she is
currently out of the country.

460
00:35:21,433 --> 00:35:23,765
This is bullshit!

461
00:37:10,475 --> 00:37:12,909
Afternoon.

462
00:37:12,944 --> 00:37:15,538
l'm looking for the body
of one Kyle Belamy.

463
00:37:23,054 --> 00:37:25,818
That's it.
Let's get out of here.

464
00:37:32,363 --> 00:37:34,490
Thanks.

465
00:37:39,804 --> 00:37:41,965
Stay close, stay close.

466
00:37:43,241 --> 00:37:45,436
Oh, you shit! Move!

467
00:37:45,476 --> 00:37:48,104
Down! Get in!
Get the car rolling! Move!

468
00:37:54,786 --> 00:37:57,687
Go! l said go!

469
00:38:07,565 --> 00:38:09,556
Go go go!

470
00:38:09,601 --> 00:38:10,898
Take the gap!
Take the gap!

471
00:38:15,073 --> 00:38:17,803
Don't fight it.

472
00:38:17,842 --> 00:38:19,867
Right, now go.
Reverse.

473
00:38:21,879 --> 00:38:23,779
An eye for an eye.

474
00:38:30,989 --> 00:38:32,513
That's it.
Keep moving.

475
00:39:02,186 --> 00:39:05,451
You sack of sweatin' soft git!

476
00:39:05,490 --> 00:39:08,015
