a tea break, guv?

480
00:39:22,040 --> 00:39:23,735
Yeah yeah, fine.

481
00:39:23,775 --> 00:39:26,573
- All right, fellas!
- Bring those two over here.

482
00:39:26,611 --> 00:39:29,239
Tea break!

483
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:32,181
All right, lads,
that's an all clear.

484
00:39:33,584 --> 00:39:36,109
A foreign banker in Brazil

485
00:39:36,154 --> 00:39:39,123
