Whoa!

1015
01:27:11,106 --> 01:27:12,300
Harry!

1016
01:27:36,731 --> 01:27:39,529
Hut, hut, hut!

1017
01:27:46,808 --> 01:27:49,140
Present... arms!

1018
01:28:27,882 --> 01:28:30,043
Goodbye, Sir.

