l could ever hurt him.

1057
01:30:48,223 --> 01:30:51,021
That's okay, Stacy.

1058
01:30:51,059 --> 01:30:53,960
l wish it were different.

1059
01:30:53,995 --> 01:30:56,896
ln a couple of years,

1060
01:30:56,931 --> 01:30:58,899
